verses.roman:
e-saba līlā varṇiyāchena vṛndāvana-dāsa
ye kichu viśeṣa ihāṅ karila prakāśa

synonyms: e-saba—all these; līlā—pastimes; varṇiyāchena—has described; vṛndāvana-dāsa—Vṛndāvana dāsa Ṭhākura; ye kichu—whatever; viśeṣa—specifics; ihāṅ—in this connection; karila—I have made; prakāśa—presentation.
translation: Śrīla Vṛndāvana dāsa Ṭhākura has described all these incidents elaborately. I have only presented the specific incidents he has not described.
